sp_returns <- sp %>% 
  group_by(Sector,Company) %>% 
  mutate(return = (Close - lag(Close, 30))/lag(Close, 30)) 

sp_returns %>% 
  filter(Sector == "Technology") %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = Date, y = return, color = Company))+
  geom_line()
